  <brief_title>Evaluation, Psychological Intervention and Follow-up Study of Anxiety and Depression in Stable COPD Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation, Psychological Intervention and Follow-up Study of Anxiety and Depression in Stable Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease Patients</official_title>
